{"id":7720,"date":"2025-12-29T13:25:18","date_gmt":"2025-12-29T06:25:18","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=7720"},"modified":"2025-12-29T17:18:31","modified_gmt":"2025-12-29T10:18:31","slug":"salicylic-acid-la-gi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/su-kien\/salicylic-acid-la-gi\/","title":{"rendered":"Salicylic Acid &#8211; Ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t cho da d\u00e0y s\u1eebng, d\u1ea7u m\u1ee5n"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Salicylic Acid (BHA) &#8211; Ngo\u00e0i t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n l\u1edbp s\u1eebng c\u1ee7a da m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nhanh ch\u00f3ng th\u00ec n\u00f3 \u0111i c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 gi\u1ea3m ti\u1ebft d\u1ea7u v\u00e0 kh\u00e1ng vi\u00eam. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i \u0111i c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch h\u1ee3p l\u00fd m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n.<\/span><\/p>\n\n<h1><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"gioi-thieu-tong-quan-ve-salicylic-acid-bha\"><\/span><b>Gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u t\u1ed5ng quan v\u1ec1 Salicylic Acid (BHA)<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h1>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Salicylic Acid (th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 BHA \u2013 Beta Hydroxy Acid) l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t acid g\u1ed1c d\u1ea7u, c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u qua b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn v\u00e0 \u0111i s\u00e2u v\u00e0o l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng trong vi\u1ec7c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n, l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a Salicylic Acid b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t v\u1ecf c\u00e2y li\u1ec5u tr\u1eafng (Willow Bark), \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng trong vi\u1ec7c h\u1ea1 s\u1ed1t v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m \u0111au t\u1eeb h\u00e0ng tr\u0103m n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Sau qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i trong m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7722\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7722\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-7722 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-1-1.webp\" alt=\"C\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a salicylic acid l\u00e0 C7H6O3\" width=\"800\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-1-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-1-1-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-1-1-768x528.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-1-1-600x413.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7722\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a salicylic acid l\u00e0 C7H6O3<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h1><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dac-diem-cua-hoat-chat-salicylic-acid-bha\"><\/span><b>\u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t Salicylic Acid (BHA)<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h1>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cong-dung-noi-bat\"><\/span><b>C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng, gi\u1ea3m b\u00edt t\u1eafc, s\u1ee3i b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111en, m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng, m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam nh\u1eb9.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho da d\u1ea7u\/m\u1ee5n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da th\u00f4 r\u00e1p, s\u1ea7n s\u00f9i, t\u1ea1o hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Gi\u00fap da h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u0103m s\u00f3c kh\u00e1c.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7723\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7723\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-7723 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-2-1.webp\" alt=\"C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng salycilic acid\" width=\"800\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-2-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-2-1-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-2-1-768x528.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-2-1-600x413.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7723\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Salicylic Acid c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n da s\u1ea7n s\u00f9i v\u00e0 gi\u00fap da tr\u00f4ng c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng h\u01a1n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"co-che-hoat-dong\"><\/span><b>C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>Tan trong d\u1ea7u:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> Salicylic Acid c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00f2a tan trong b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn, gi\u00fap \u0111i s\u00e2u v\u00e0o l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>Keratolytic (bong s\u1eebng):<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft, gi\u00fap da th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng v\u00e0 m\u1ecbn h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>Kh\u00e1ng vi\u00eam:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> c\u00f3 c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn aspirin, mang t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam nh\u1eb9, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ecf.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>Ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba m\u1ee5n t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> khi l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng v\u00e0 b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng, nguy c\u01a1 h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5n gi\u1ea3m \u0111i.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dang-bao-che-thuong-gap\"><\/span><b>D\u1ea1ng b\u00e0o ch\u1ebf th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>Toner\/serum g\u1ed1c n\u01b0\u1edbc:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 th\u1ea5p (0,5\u20132%) ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p d\u00f9ng h\u1eb1ng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba m\u1ee5n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>Gel\/kem ch\u1ea5m m\u1ee5n:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 cao h\u01a1n, t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp l\u00ean nh\u00e2n m\u1ee5n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>S\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba v\u00e0 t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t, d\u1ea1ng r\u1eeda tr\u00f4i ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba tr\u00ean da<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>Peel chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 cao h\u01a1n (10\u201330%) ch\u1ec9 d\u00f9ng trong c\u01a1 s\u1edf th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1m s\u00e1t chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h1><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"huong-dan-su-dung-salicylic-acid\"><\/span><b>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Salicylic Acid<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h1>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"doi-tuong-su-dung-la-ai\"><\/span><b>\u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng l\u00e0 ai?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da d\u1ea7u\/da h\u1ed7n h\u1ee3p thi\u00ean d\u1ea7u, l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng to, b\u00f3ng nh\u1eddn.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111en, \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng, b\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng (comedones); m\u1ee5n l\u01b0ng\/ng\u1ef1c.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u00e0y s\u1eebng, da s\u1ea7n, s\u1eebng h\u00f3a quanh l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng; keratosis pilaris (da \u201cg\u00e0\u201d).<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7724\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7724\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-7724 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-3-1.webp\" alt=\"Salicylic Acid d\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho c\u1ea3 body\" width=\"800\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-3-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-3-1-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-3-1-768x528.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-3-1-600x413.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7724\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 m\u1eb7t, SA c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng cho m\u1ee5n c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 d\u00e0y s\u1eebng nang l\u00f4ng<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da vi\u00eam nang l\u00f4ng\/l\u00f4ng m\u1ecdc ng\u01b0\u1ee3c (ingrown hair) (m\u1eb7t, n\u00e1ch, bikini, body).<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u00e2m sau vi\u00eam (PIH): BHA h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 gi\u1ea3m t\u1eafc ngh\u1ebdn, ng\u0103n m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam m\u1edbi v\u00e0 t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft gi\u00fap th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o da v\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf l\u1edbp bi\u1ec3u b\u00ec th\u00e2m s\u1ea1m do melanin.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cach-su-dung-lieu-luong-nhu-the-nao\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, li\u1ec1u l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u01b0u \u00fd: \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi b\u00f4i thoa tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n (OTC) khung n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 h\u1ee3p chu\u1ea9n FDA c\u1ee7a salicylic acid cho s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n kh\u00f4ng k\u00ea \u0111\u01a1n l\u00e0 m\u1ee9c 0,5\u20132%. T\u1ee9c l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9a n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 cao h\u01a1n 2% \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 tham v\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a chuy\u00ean gia v\u00e0 b\u00e1c s\u0129.<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u1ea3ng tham kh\u1ea3o c\u00e1ch d\u00f9ng theo n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 SA\u00a0<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7725\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7725\" style=\"width: 971px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-7725 \" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Anh-4-1.webp\" alt=\" B\u1ea3ng \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a Salicylic Acid (BHA) theo n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m\" width=\"971\" height=\"607\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Anh-4-1.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Anh-4-1-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Anh-4-1-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Anh-4-1-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 971px) 100vw, 971px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7725\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">B\u1ea3ng \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a Salicylic Acid (BHA) theo n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-hop-salicylic-acid-sao-cho-hieu-qua\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p Salicylic Acid sao cho hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>Salicylic Acid + Niacinamide:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t d\u1ea7u, se l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng v\u00e0 c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>Salicylic Acid + Sulfur:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i gi\u1ea3m b\u00edt t\u1eafc + kh\u00e1ng vi\u00eam cho da d\u1ea7u m\u1ee5n. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i v\u00e0ng trong kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gom c\u1ed3i m\u1ee5n nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i th\u00e2m.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/kem-cham-mun-gsc\/\">Ch\u1ea5m m\u1ee5n Sulfur + SA GSC+.<\/a><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>Salicylic Acid + Retinol (lu\u00e2n phi\u00ean c\u00e1ch ng\u00e0y):<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> gi\u1ea3m m\u1ee5n v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng l\u00e3o h\u00f3a, nh\u01b0ng <\/span><b>tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u00f4ng d\u00f9ng c\u00f9ng l\u00fac<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh k\u00edch \u1ee9ng. Kh\u00f4ng khuy\u1ebfn kh\u00edch n\u1ebfu da ch\u01b0a quen c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t active m\u1ea1nh ho\u1eb7c da m\u1ecfng y\u1ebfu.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>Salicylic Acid + AHA (Glycolic, Lactic):<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> combo peel s\u00e2u h\u01a1n, th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ea5y trong peel chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p. <\/span><b>(Kh\u00f4ng khuy\u1ebfn kh\u00edch t\u1ef1 peel s\u00e2u t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0)<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>Salicylic Acid + Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu (HA, Panthenol, Allantoin, Centella):<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m kh\u00f4 r\u00e1t v\u00e0 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng da.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"luu-y-chong-chi-dinh\"><\/span><b>L\u01b0u \u00fd &amp; Ch\u1ed1ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh:\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean d\u00f9ng SA cho: da qu\u00e1 nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, da kh\u00f4 bong tr\u00f3c n\u1eb7ng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng aspirin (do c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac li\u00ean quan).<\/p>\n<p>Tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng peel n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 cao (BHA&gt;2%) khi ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a chuy\u00ean gia<\/p>\n<p>Tr\u00e1nh ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng l\u00fac v\u1edbi: retinoid m\u1ea1nh, benzoyl peroxide, AHA n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 cao \u2192 d\u1ec5 g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/p>\n<p>Ng\u01b0ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ecf r\u00e1t, ch\u00e2m ch\u00edch k\u00e9o d\u00e0i.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef mang thai v\u00e0 cho con b\u00fa c\u00f3 d\u00f9ng SA \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng?\u00a0<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m thu\u1ea7n peel Salicylic Acid (BHA):Ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef c\u00f3 thai\/\u0111ang cho con b\u00fa n\u00ean tham kh\u1ea3o \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi d\u00f9ng n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 cao ho\u1eb7c peel.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n c\u00f3 ph\u1ee9c h\u1ee3p c\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n c\u1ea7n c\u1ea9n tr\u1ecdng l\u01b0u \u00fd, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 BHA&lt;2% (n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng k\u00ea \u0111\u01a1n chu\u1ea9n FDA) v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i tham kh\u1ea3o \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia ho\u1eb7c b\u00e1c s\u0129 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>T\u00e0i li\u1ec7u tham kh\u1ea3o:\u00a0<\/b><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Hedner, T., &amp; Everts, B. (1998). The early clinical history of salicylates in rheumatology and pain. Clinical Rheumatology, 17(1), 17\u201325. <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/doi.org\/10.1007\/BF01450953\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">https:\/\/doi.org\/10.1007\/BF01450953<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">U.S. Food and Drug Administration Over-the-Counter (OTC) Monograph M006: Topical Acne Drug Products for Over-the-Counter Human Use (Posted November 23, 2021) 1 Part A-General Provisions Part A-General Provisions \u00a7 M006.1 Scope<\/span><\/i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">. (n.d.). Retrieved October 3, 2025, from <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.accessdata.fda.gov\/drugsatfda_docs\/omuf\/monographs\/OTC%20Monograph_M006-Topical%20Acne%20drug%20products%20for%20OTC%20Human%20Use%2011.23.2021.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">https:\/\/www.accessdata.fda.gov\/drugsatfda_docs\/omuf\/monographs\/OTC%20Monograph_M006-Topical%20Acne%20drug%20products%20for%20OTC%20Human%20Use%2011.23.2021.pdf<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ngan, V. (2005). <\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Salicylic acid | DermNet NZ<\/span><\/i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">. Dermnetnz.org. https:\/\/dermnetnz.org\/topics\/salicylic-acid<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u00e2u, L. (2025). <\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">BHA<\/span><\/i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">. Nh\u00e0 Thu\u1ed1c Long Ch\u00e2u. https:\/\/nhathuoclongchau.com.vn\/thanh-phan\/bha<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Salicylic Acid (BHA) &#8211; Ngo\u00e0i t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n l\u1edbp s\u1eebng c\u1ee7a da m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nhanh ch\u00f3ng th\u00ec n\u00f3 \u0111i c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 gi\u1ea3m ti\u1ebft d\u1ea7u v\u00e0 kh\u00e1ng vi\u00eam. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i \u0111i c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch h\u1ee3p l\u00fd m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":12,"featured_media":7721,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-7720","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-su-kien"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7720","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/12"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=7720"}],"version-history":[{"count":9,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7720\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":7930,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7720\/revisions\/7930"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/7721"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=7720"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=7720"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=7720"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}